---
import products from "@/public/assets/products.png"
---

<section class="bg-white w-full h-fit py-6 lg:py-12 relative container">
  <img
    src={products.src}
    alt="decoration"
    class="absolute top-0 w-32 right-0"
  />
  <h3 class="text-primary font-semibold text-lg mt-28 lg:mt-0">Products</h3>
  <h2 class="max-w-md text-4xl font-bold mt-6">
    Suite of Products for all chainless
  </h2>
  <div class="grid grid-cols-4 w-full gap-12 mt-10 lg:mt-16">
    <div
      class="col-span-full md:col-span-2 lg:col-span-1 flex flex-col items-start"
    >
      <div class="p-2 rounded-full bg-[#F6F4EF]">
        <svg
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          fill="none"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          stroke-width="1.5"
          stroke="currentColor"
          class="w-6 h-6 text-primary"
        >
          <path
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            d="M3.75 13.5l10.5-11.25L12 10.5h8.25L9.75 21.75 12 13.5H3.75z"
          ></path>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h4 class="font-medium text-lg my-3">Lightning Fast</h4>
      <p>
        From direct integrations with card networks and banks to checkout flows
        in the browser, we operate on and optimize at every level of the
        financial stack.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div
      class="col-span-full md:col-span-2 lg:col-span-1 flex flex-col items-start"
    >
      <div class="p-2 rounded-full bg-[#F6F4EF]">
        <svg
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          fill="none"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          stroke-width="1.5"
          stroke="currentColor"
          class="w-6 h-6 text-primary"
        >
          <path
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            d="M11.42 15.17L17.25 21A2.652 2.652 0 0021 17.25l-5.877-5.877M11.42 15.17l2.496-3.03c.317-.384.74-.626 1.208-.766M11.42 15.17l-4.655 5.653a2.548 2.548 0 11-3.586-3.586l6.837-5.63m5.108-.233c.55-.164 1.163-.188 1.743-.14a4.5 4.5 0 004.486-6.336l-3.276 3.277a3.004 3.004 0 01-2.25-2.25l3.276-3.276a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.336 4.486c.091 1.076-.071 2.264-.904 2.95l-.102.085m-1.745 1.437L5.909 7.5H4.5L2.25 3.75l1.5-1.5L7.5 4.5v1.409l4.26 4.26m-1.745 1.437l1.745-1.437m6.615 8.206L15.75 15.75M4.867 19.125h.008v.008h-.008v-.008z"
          ></path>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h4 class="font-medium text-lg my-3">Dev Tools</h4>
      <p>
        We release hundreds of features and improvements each year to help you
        stay ahead of industry shifts. (On average, we deploy our production API
        16x per day.)
      </p>
    </div>
    <div
      class="col-span-full md:col-span-2 lg:col-span-1 flex flex-col items-start"
    >
      <div class="p-2 rounded-full bg-[#F6F4EF]">
        <svg
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          fill="none"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          stroke-width="1.5"
          stroke="currentColor"
          class="w-6 h-6 text-primary"
        >
          <path
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            d="M12 6v12m-3-2.818l.879.659c1.171.879 3.07.879 4.242 0 1.172-.879 1.172-2.303 0-3.182C13.536 12.219 12.768 12 12 12c-.725 0-1.45-.22-2.003-.659-1.106-.879-1.106-2.303 0-3.182s2.9-.879 4.006 0l.415.33M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"
          ></path>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h4 class="font-medium text-lg my-3">Gas Fees</h4>
      <p>
        Our systems operate with 99.99%+ uptime and are highly scalable and
        redundant. Stripe is certified to the highest compliance standards.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div
      class="col-span-full md:col-span-2 lg:col-span-1 flex flex-col items-start"
    >
      <div class="p-2 rounded-full bg-[#F6F4EF]">
        <svg
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          fill="none"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          stroke-width="1.5"
          stroke="currentColor"
          class="w-6 h-6 text-primary"
        >
          <path
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            d="M3.75 13.5l10.5-11.25L12 10.5h8.25L9.75 21.75 12 13.5H3.75z"
          ></path>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h4 class="font-medium text-lg my-3">Peer-to-Peer</h4>
      <p>
        Our machine learning models train on billions of data points and help
        increase revenue across conversion, fraud, revenue recovery, and more.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
